# Cursor AI Configuration for New CMS Project

# This file contains project-specific rules and preferences for Cursor AI

# Project Context
# This is a PHP/MySQL CMS with Elementor-style page builder
# Main technologies: PHP 7+, MySQL, jQuery, Vanilla JavaScript

# Code Style Preferences
- Use PSR-12 coding standards for PHP where applicable
- Use ES6+ JavaScript syntax
- Always use prepared statements for database queries
- Follow existing code patterns in the project

# API Configuration
# If you need to configure Z AI API key, add it to Cursor Settings:
# Settings > Features > AI > API Keys > Add Z AI API Key

# Project Structure Notes
# - Backend: PHP in root and admin/ directories
# - Frontend: JavaScript in assets/ directory
# - Widgets: Extend WidgetBase class
# - Controls: Extend BaseControl class








